{
  "stem": "14156.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The crates were full of the ammunition and full of guns and full of-- you know, ready for the war, what eventually would happen in Israel.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so we finally came to Haifa.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I holler down-- people down-- and said, please, call-- call-- tell [INAUDIBLE], tell my uncle and my aunt that I'm here, and I'm-- I'm-- I'm alive.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I'm from here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't know where I'm going, but-- They brought us to Atlit-- what was a famous camp and is, today, still-- and kept us there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And-- you know, they make sure that we are clean, that there is no-- no sickness on us to-- to-- to be--",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--contagious to somebody else.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know-- one thing don't-- I always won't forget.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When finally my-- my cousin-- she was a girl cousin-- [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Tovah ?] is her name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She picked me up, and I had papers already they gave us, you know, that we are legal in Palestine.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She passed away, too, long ago-- well, 20 years or so ago, on breast cancer, but-- When I came, and I met my uncle-- Uncle Max.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was-- my-- I was his godchild.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we met, and I was going to kiss him, and he wouldn't.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was afraid that I had some sickness and that I had, you know, brought with me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he stood away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, Uncle Max, don't worry about it!",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm-- I'm OK-- I'm clean!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They wouldn't let me out without it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OK, then, later he understood.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and I guess he was OK.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, from there on, I lived with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And what came after that?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Oh, we met-- everybody came and-- and-- and looked me over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "People came.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I know a-- a woman came to me, and I was together with the man.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
